{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT for patients in psychotherapeutic treatment.",
    "In this case study, a patient who had been in psychoanalytic therapy for several months turned to ChatGPT to bridge the time between sessions, as well as during the therapist's vacation.",
    "Before describing the case studies, I would like to share an interesting observation.",
    "While researching this paper, I asked the chatbot a wide variety of questions.",
    "Among them was why Sigmund Freud would recommend ChatGPT."
  ]
}